{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"These are grim economic times,"},{"time":3000,"text":"fellow TEDsters, grim economic times indeed."},{"time":6000,"text":"And so, I would like to cheer you up"},{"time":9000,"text":"with one of the great, albeit largely unknown,"},{"time":12000,"text":"commercial success stories"},{"time":14000,"text":"of the past 20 years."},{"time":16000,"text":"Comparable, in its own very peculiar way,"},{"time":19000,"text":"to the achievements of Microsoft or Google."},{"time":22000,"text":"And it's an industry which has bucked the current recession"},{"time":25000,"text":"with equanimity."},{"time":27000,"text":"I refer to organized crime."}]},{"cues":[{"time":30000,"text":"Now organized crime has been around"},{"time":32000,"text":"for a very long time, I hear you say,"},{"time":35000,"text":"and these would be wise words, indeed."},{"time":37000,"text":"But in the last two decades,"},{"time":40000,"text":"it has experienced an unprecedented expansion,"},{"time":43000,"text":"now accounting for roughly 15 percent"},{"time":47000,"text":"of the world's GDP."},{"time":49000,"text":"I like to call it the Global Shadow Economy,"},{"time":52000,"text":"or McMafia, for short."}]},{"cues":[{"time":55000,"text":"So what triggered this extraordinary growth"},{"time":58000,"text":"in cross-border crime?"},{"time":60000,"text":"Well, of course, there is globalization,"},{"time":62000,"text":"technology, communications, all that stuff,"},{"time":65000,"text":"which we'll talk about a little bit later."},{"time":68000,"text":"But first, I would like to take you back"},{"time":71000,"text":"to this event:"},{"time":73000,"text":"the collapse of communism."},{"time":75000,"text":"All across Eastern Europe, a most momentous episode"},{"time":79000,"text":"in our post-war history."}]},{"cues":[{"time":81000,"text":"Now it's time for full disclosure."},{"time":84000,"text":"This event meant a great deal to me personally."},{"time":87000,"text":"I had started smuggling books across the Iron Curtain"},{"time":91000,"text":"to Democratic opposition groups in Eastern Europe,"},{"time":93000,"text":"like Solidarity in Poland,"},{"time":95000,"text":"when I was in my teens."},{"time":97000,"text":"I then started writing about Eastern Europe,"},{"time":101000,"text":"and eventually I became the BBC's chief correspondent for the region,"},{"time":105000,"text":"which is what I was doing in 1989."},{"time":109000,"text":"And so when 425 million people"},{"time":113000,"text":"finally won the right"},{"time":115000,"text":"to choose their own governments,"},{"time":117000,"text":"I was ecstatic,"},{"time":120000,"text":"but I was also a touch worried"},{"time":122000,"text":"about some of the nastier things"},{"time":124000,"text":"lurking behind the wall."}]},{"cues":[{"time":126000,"text":"It wasn't long, for example,"},{"time":128000,"text":"before ethnic nationalism"},{"time":130000,"text":"reared its bloody head"},{"time":132000,"text":"in Yugoslavia."},{"time":134000,"text":"And amongst the chaos,"},{"time":136000,"text":"amidst the euphoria,"},{"time":138000,"text":"it took me a little while to understand"},{"time":140000,"text":"that some of the people who had wielded power"},{"time":143000,"text":"before 1989, in Eastern Europe,"},{"time":147000,"text":"continued to do so after the revolutions there."},{"time":151000,"text":"Obviously there were characters like this."},{"time":155000,"text":"But there were also some more unexpected people"},{"time":159000,"text":"who played a critical role in what was going on in Eastern Europe."}]},{"cues":[{"time":163000,"text":"Like this character. Remember these guys?"},{"time":166000,"text":"They used to win the gold medals in weightlifting"},{"time":168000,"text":"and wrestling, every four years in the Olympics,"},{"time":171000,"text":"and they were the great celebrities of communism,"},{"time":174000,"text":"with a fabulous lifestyle to go with it."},{"time":177000,"text":"They used to get great apartments in the center of town,"},{"time":179000,"text":"casual sex on tap,"},{"time":181000,"text":"and they could travel to the West very freely,"},{"time":184000,"text":"which was a great luxury at the time."},{"time":187000,"text":"It may come as a surprise, but they played a critical role"},{"time":191000,"text":"in the emergence of the market economy"},{"time":193000,"text":"in Eastern Europe."},{"time":195000,"text":"Or as I like to call them, they are"},{"time":197000,"text":"the midwives of capitalism."},{"time":199000,"text":"Here are some of those same weightlifters"},{"time":202000,"text":"after their 1989 makeover."}]},{"cues":[{"time":205000,"text":"Now in Bulgaria --"},{"time":208000,"text":"this photograph was taken in Bulgaria --"},{"time":210000,"text":"when communism collapsed all over Eastern Europe,"},{"time":213000,"text":"it wasn't just communism;"},{"time":215000,"text":"it was the state that collapsed as well."},{"time":217000,"text":"That means your police force wasn't working."},{"time":219000,"text":"The court system wasn't functioning properly."},{"time":222000,"text":"So what was a business man in the brave new world"},{"time":227000,"text":"of East European capitalism going to do"},{"time":229000,"text":"to make sure that his contracts would be honored?"},{"time":233000,"text":"Well, he would turn to people who were called, rather prosaically"},{"time":236000,"text":"by sociologists, privatized law enforcement agencies."},{"time":240000,"text":"We prefer to know them as the mafia."},{"time":244000,"text":"And in Bulgaria, the mafia was soon joined"},{"time":247000,"text":"with 14,000 people"},{"time":249000,"text":"who were sacked from their jobs in the security services"},{"time":253000,"text":"between 1989 and 1991."}]},{"cues":[{"time":255000,"text":"Now, when your state is collapsing,"},{"time":259000,"text":"your economy is heading south at a rate of knots,"},{"time":262000,"text":"the last people you want coming on to the labor market"},{"time":265000,"text":"are 14,000 men and women whose chief skills"},{"time":268000,"text":"are surveillance,"},{"time":270000,"text":"are smuggling, building underground networks"},{"time":273000,"text":"and killing people."},{"time":276000,"text":"But that's what happened all over Eastern Europe."},{"time":279000,"text":"Now, when I was working in the 1990s,"},{"time":284000,"text":"I spent most of the time covering"},{"time":287000,"text":"the appalling conflict in Yugoslavia."}]},{"cues":[{"time":290000,"text":"And I couldn't help notice"},{"time":292000,"text":"that the people who were perpetrating the appalling atrocities,"},{"time":296000,"text":"the paramilitary organizations,"},{"time":299000,"text":"were actually the same people running"},{"time":301000,"text":"the organized criminal syndicates."},{"time":304000,"text":"And I came to think that behind the violence"},{"time":308000,"text":"lay a sinister criminal enterprise."},{"time":311000,"text":"And so I resolved to travel around the world"},{"time":315000,"text":"examining this global criminal underworld"},{"time":318000,"text":"by talking to policemen,"},{"time":320000,"text":"by talking to victims, by talking to consumers"},{"time":323000,"text":"of illicit goods and services."},{"time":325000,"text":"But above all else, by talking to the gangsters themselves."}]},{"cues":[{"time":330000,"text":"And the Balkans was a fabulous place to start."},{"time":333000,"text":"Why? Well of course"},{"time":335000,"text":"there was the issue of law and order collapsing,"},{"time":337000,"text":"but also, as they say in the retail trade,"},{"time":339000,"text":"it's location, location, location."},{"time":343000,"text":"And what I noticed at the beginning of my research"},{"time":345000,"text":"that the Balkans had turned into a vast transit zone"},{"time":350000,"text":"for illicit goods and services coming from all over the world."},{"time":353000,"text":"Heroin, cocaine,"},{"time":355000,"text":"women being trafficked into prostitution"},{"time":358000,"text":"and precious minerals."}]},{"cues":[{"time":360000,"text":"And where were they heading?"},{"time":362000,"text":"The European Union, which by now"},{"time":364000,"text":"was beginning to reap the benefits of globalization,"},{"time":368000,"text":"transforming it into"},{"time":370000,"text":"the most affluent consumer market in history,"},{"time":373000,"text":"eventually comprising some 500 million people."},{"time":376000,"text":"And a significant minority"},{"time":379000,"text":"of those 500 million people"},{"time":381000,"text":"like to spend some of their leisure time and spare cash"},{"time":384000,"text":"sleeping with prostitutes,"},{"time":386000,"text":"sticking 50 Euro notes up their nose"},{"time":389000,"text":"and employing illegal migrant laborers."}]},{"cues":[{"time":392000,"text":"Now, organized crime in a globalizing world"},{"time":396000,"text":"operates in the same way as any other business."},{"time":398000,"text":"It has zones of production,"},{"time":401000,"text":"like Afghanistan and Columbia."},{"time":404000,"text":"It has zones of distribution,"},{"time":406000,"text":"like Mexico and the Balkans."},{"time":409000,"text":"And then, of course, it has zones of consumption,"},{"time":413000,"text":"like the European Union, Japan"},{"time":415000,"text":"and of course, the United States."},{"time":418000,"text":"The zones of production and distribution"},{"time":421000,"text":"tend to lie in the developing world,"},{"time":424000,"text":"and they are often threatened by appalling violence"},{"time":428000,"text":"and bloodshed."}]},{"cues":[{"time":430000,"text":"Take Mexico, for example."},{"time":432000,"text":"Six thousand people killed there in the last 18 months"},{"time":436000,"text":"as a direct consequence of the cocaine trade."},{"time":440000,"text":"But what about the Democratic Republic of Congo?"},{"time":444000,"text":"Since 1998, five million people have died there."},{"time":450000,"text":"It's not a conflict you read about much in the newspapers,"},{"time":452000,"text":"but it's the biggest conflict on this planet"},{"time":455000,"text":"since the Second World War."},{"time":457000,"text":"And why is it? Because mafias from all around the world"},{"time":460000,"text":"cooperate with local paramilitaries"},{"time":463000,"text":"in order to seize the supplies"},{"time":466000,"text":"of the rich mineral resources"},{"time":468000,"text":"of the region."}]},{"cues":[{"time":470000,"text":"In the year 2000, 80 percent of the world's coltan"},{"time":474000,"text":"was sourced to the killing fields"},{"time":476000,"text":"of the eastern Democratic Republic of Congo."},{"time":480000,"text":"Now, coltan you will find in almost every mobile phone,"},{"time":484000,"text":"in almost every laptop"},{"time":486000,"text":"and games console."},{"time":488000,"text":"The Congolese war lords were selling this stuff to the mafia"},{"time":491000,"text":"in exchange for weapons,"},{"time":493000,"text":"and the mafia would then sell it on to Western markets."},{"time":497000,"text":"And it is this Western desire"},{"time":499000,"text":"to consume"},{"time":501000,"text":"that is the primary driver"},{"time":504000,"text":"of international organized crime."}]},{"cues":[{"time":507000,"text":"Now, let me show you some of my friends in action,"},{"time":511000,"text":"caught conveniently on film by the Italian police,"},{"time":514000,"text":"and smuggling duty-not-paid cigarettes."},{"time":517000,"text":"Now, cigarettes out the factory gate are very cheap."},{"time":520000,"text":"The European Union then imposes the highest taxes on them in the world."},{"time":524000,"text":"So if you can smuggle them into the E.U.,"},{"time":527000,"text":"there are very handsome profits to be made,"},{"time":530000,"text":"and I want to show you this to demonstrate"},{"time":532000,"text":"the type of resources available to these groups."}]},{"cues":[{"time":535000,"text":"This boat is worth one million Euros when it's new."},{"time":539000,"text":"And it's the fastest thing on European waters."},{"time":543000,"text":"From 1994, for seven years,"},{"time":546000,"text":"20 of these boats"},{"time":548000,"text":"made the trip across the Adriatic,"},{"time":551000,"text":"from Montenegro to Italy, every single night."},{"time":554000,"text":"And as a consequence of this trade,"},{"time":556000,"text":"Britain alone lost eight billion dollars in revenue."},{"time":561000,"text":"And instead that money went to underwrite the wars in Yugoslavia"},{"time":565000,"text":"and line the pockets of unscrupulous individuals."}]},{"cues":[{"time":569000,"text":"Now Italian police, when this trade started,"},{"time":572000,"text":"had just two boats which could go at the same speed."},{"time":576000,"text":"And this is very important, because the only way you can catch these guys"},{"time":578000,"text":"is if they run out of gas."},{"time":581000,"text":"Sometimes the gangsters would bring with them"},{"time":583000,"text":"women being trafficked into prostitution,"},{"time":586000,"text":"and if the police intervened, they would hurl"},{"time":588000,"text":"the women into the sea"},{"time":591000,"text":"so that the police had to go and save them from drowning,"},{"time":593000,"text":"rather than chasing the bad guys."}]},{"cues":[{"time":597000,"text":"So I have shown you this to demonstrate"},{"time":600000,"text":"how many boats, how many vessels it takes"},{"time":602000,"text":"to catch one of these guys."},{"time":604000,"text":"And the answer is six vessels."},{"time":606000,"text":"And remember, 20 of these speed boats"},{"time":609000,"text":"were coming across the Adriatic"},{"time":611000,"text":"every single night."},{"time":613000,"text":"So what were these guys doing with all the money they were making?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":617000,"text":"Well, this is where we come to globalization,"},{"time":621000,"text":"because that was not just the deregulation of global trade."},{"time":624000,"text":"It was the liberalization of international financial markets."},{"time":627000,"text":"And boy, did that make it easy"},{"time":630000,"text":"for the money launderers."},{"time":632000,"text":"The last two decades have been the champagne era"},{"time":635000,"text":"for dirty lucre."}]},{"cues":[{"time":637000,"text":"In the 1990s, we saw financial centers around the world"},{"time":641000,"text":"competing for their business,"},{"time":644000,"text":"and there was simply no effective mechanism"},{"time":646000,"text":"to prevent money laundering."},{"time":648000,"text":"And a lot of licit banks were also happy"},{"time":651000,"text":"to accept deposits"},{"time":654000,"text":"from very dubious sources"},{"time":656000,"text":"without questions being asked."}]},{"cues":[{"time":659000,"text":"But at the heart of this, is the offshore banking network."},{"time":663000,"text":"Now these things"},{"time":666000,"text":"are an essential part of the money laundering parade,"},{"time":669000,"text":"and if you want to do something about illegal tax evasion"},{"time":673000,"text":"and transnational organized crime, money laundering,"},{"time":677000,"text":"you have to get rid of them."},{"time":679000,"text":"On a positive note, we at last have someone in the White House"},{"time":682000,"text":"who has consistently spoken out"},{"time":685000,"text":"against these corrosive entities."}]},{"cues":[{"time":688000,"text":"And if anyone is concerned about what I believe"},{"time":692000,"text":"is the necessity for"},{"time":695000,"text":"new legislation, regulation, effective regulation,"},{"time":698000,"text":"I say, let's take a look at Bernie Madoff,"},{"time":702000,"text":"who is now going to be spending the rest of his life in jail."},{"time":706000,"text":"Bernie Madoff stole 65 billion dollars."},{"time":712000,"text":"That puts him up there on the Olympus of gangsters"},{"time":715000,"text":"with the Colombian cartels"},{"time":717000,"text":"and the major Russian crime syndicates,"},{"time":720000,"text":"but he did this for decades"},{"time":722000,"text":"in the very heart of Wall Street,"},{"time":724000,"text":"and no regulator picked up on it."},{"time":727000,"text":"So how many other Madoffs are there on Wall Street"},{"time":730000,"text":"or in the city of London,"},{"time":732000,"text":"fleecing ordinary folk"},{"time":734000,"text":"and money laundering?"},{"time":736000,"text":"Well I can tell you, it's quite a few of them."}]},{"cues":[{"time":740000,"text":"Let me go on to the 101 of international organized crime now."},{"time":744000,"text":"And that is narcotics. Our second marijuana farm photograph for the morning."},{"time":748000,"text":"This one, however, is in central British Columbia"},{"time":751000,"text":"where I photographed it."},{"time":753000,"text":"It's one of the tens of thousands"},{"time":755000,"text":"of mom-and-pop grow-ops in B.C."},{"time":758000,"text":"which ensure that over five percent"},{"time":761000,"text":"of the province's GDP is accounted for by this trade."}]},{"cues":[{"time":765000,"text":"Now, I was taken by inspector Brian Cantera,"},{"time":770000,"text":"of the Royal Canadian Mounted Police,"},{"time":772000,"text":"to a cavernous warehouse east of Vancouver"},{"time":774000,"text":"to see some of the goods which are regularly confiscated"},{"time":778000,"text":"by the RCMP"},{"time":780000,"text":"from the smugglers who are sending it,"},{"time":782000,"text":"of course, down south to the United States"},{"time":785000,"text":"where there is an insatiable market"},{"time":787000,"text":"for B.C. Bud, as it's called,"},{"time":790000,"text":"in part because it's marketed as organic,"},{"time":792000,"text":"which of course goes down very well in California."},{"time":796000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":798000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":799000,"text":"Now, even by the police's admission,"},{"time":802000,"text":"this makes not a dent in the profits, really,"},{"time":807000,"text":"of the major exporters."},{"time":809000,"text":"Since the beginning of globalization,"},{"time":811000,"text":"the global narcotics market has expanded enormously."},{"time":815000,"text":"There has, however, been no concomitant increase"},{"time":818000,"text":"in the resources available"},{"time":821000,"text":"to police forces."}]},{"cues":[{"time":823000,"text":"This, however, may all be about to change,"},{"time":828000,"text":"because something very strange is going on."},{"time":830000,"text":"The United Nations recognized"},{"time":832000,"text":"earlier this -- it was last month actually --"},{"time":835000,"text":"that Canada has become a key area of distribution and production"},{"time":841000,"text":"of ecstasy and other synthetic drugs."}]},{"cues":[{"time":845000,"text":"Interestingly, the market share"},{"time":847000,"text":"of heroin and cocaine is going down,"},{"time":850000,"text":"because the pills are getting ever better at reproducing their highs."},{"time":855000,"text":"Now that is a game changer,"},{"time":859000,"text":"because it shifts production away from the developing world"},{"time":863000,"text":"and into the Western world."},{"time":867000,"text":"When that happens, it is a trend"},{"time":869000,"text":"which is set to overwhelm our policing capacity in the West."},{"time":873000,"text":"The drugs policy which we've had in place for 40 years"},{"time":877000,"text":"is long overdue for a very serious rethink,"},{"time":882000,"text":"in my opinion."}]},{"cues":[{"time":884000,"text":"Now, the recession."},{"time":886000,"text":"Well, organized crime has already adapted"},{"time":888000,"text":"very well to the recession."},{"time":890000,"text":"Not surprising, the most opportunistic industry"},{"time":892000,"text":"in the whole world."},{"time":894000,"text":"And it has no rules to its regulatory system."},{"time":898000,"text":"Except, of course, it has two business risks:"},{"time":902000,"text":"arrest by law enforcement,"},{"time":904000,"text":"which is, frankly, the least of their worries,"},{"time":906000,"text":"and competition from other groups,"},{"time":909000,"text":"i.e. a bullet in the back of the head."}]},{"cues":[{"time":911000,"text":"What they've done is they've shifted their operations."},{"time":914000,"text":"People don't smoke as much dope, or visit prostitutes quite so frequently"},{"time":918000,"text":"during a recession."},{"time":920000,"text":"And so instead, they have invaded financial"},{"time":922000,"text":"and corporate crime in a big way,"},{"time":924000,"text":"but above all, two sectors,"},{"time":926000,"text":"and that is counterfeit goods"},{"time":929000,"text":"and cybercrime."},{"time":931000,"text":"And it's been terribly successful."},{"time":933000,"text":"I would like to introduce you to Mr. Pringle."},{"time":936000,"text":"Or perhaps I should say, more accurately, Señor Pringle."}]},{"cues":[{"time":940000,"text":"I was introduced to this bit of kit by a Brazilian cybercriminal."},{"time":944000,"text":"We sat in a car on the Avenue Paulista"},{"time":946000,"text":"in São Paulo, together."},{"time":948000,"text":"Hooked it up to my laptop,"},{"time":950000,"text":"and within about five minutes he had penetrated"},{"time":953000,"text":"the computer security system"},{"time":955000,"text":"of a major Brazilian bank."},{"time":958000,"text":"It's really not that difficult."},{"time":960000,"text":"And it's actually much easier because"},{"time":963000,"text":"the fascinating thing about cybercrime"},{"time":965000,"text":"is that it's not so much the technology."}]},{"cues":[{"time":969000,"text":"The key to cybercrime is what we call social engineering."},{"time":973000,"text":"Or to use the technical term for it,"},{"time":975000,"text":"there's one born every minute."},{"time":978000,"text":"You would not believe how easy it is"},{"time":981000,"text":"to persuade people to do things with their computers"},{"time":984000,"text":"which are objectively not in their interest."},{"time":987000,"text":"And it was very soon"},{"time":989000,"text":"when the cybercriminals learned that the quickest way to do this,"},{"time":991000,"text":"of course, the quickest way to a person's wallet"},{"time":995000,"text":"is through the promise of sex and love."}]},{"cues":[{"time":998000,"text":"I expect some of you remember the ILOVEYOU virus,"},{"time":1001000,"text":"one of the very great worldwide viruses that came."},{"time":1005000,"text":"I was very fortunate when the ILOVEYOU virus came out,"},{"time":1008000,"text":"because the first person I received it from"},{"time":1011000,"text":"was an ex-girlfriend of mine."},{"time":1013000,"text":"Now, she harbored all sorts of sentiments and emotions towards me at the time,"},{"time":1018000,"text":"but love was not amongst them."},{"time":1020000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":1022000,"text":"And so as soon as I saw this drop into my inbox,"},{"time":1026000,"text":"I dispatched it hastily to the recycle bin"},{"time":1029000,"text":"and spared myself a very nasty infection."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1034000,"text":"So, cybercrime, do watch out for it."},{"time":1038000,"text":"One thing that we do know that the Internet is doing"},{"time":1040000,"text":"is the Internet is assisting these guys."},{"time":1043000,"text":"These are mosquitos who carry the malarial parasite"},{"time":1046000,"text":"which infests our blood when the mosy has had a free meal"},{"time":1050000,"text":"at our expense."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1052000,"text":"Now, Artesunate is a very effective drug"},{"time":1055000,"text":"at destroying the parasite in the early days"},{"time":1058000,"text":"of infection."},{"time":1060000,"text":"But over the past year or so,"},{"time":1062000,"text":"researchers in Cambodia have discovered"},{"time":1065000,"text":"that what's happening is"},{"time":1068000,"text":"the malarial parasite is developing a resistance."},{"time":1071000,"text":"And they fear that the reason why it's developing a resistance"},{"time":1074000,"text":"is because Cambodians can't afford the drugs on the commercial market,"},{"time":1078000,"text":"and so they buy it from the Internet."},{"time":1081000,"text":"And these pills contain only low doses"},{"time":1083000,"text":"of the active ingredient."},{"time":1085000,"text":"Which is why"},{"time":1087000,"text":"the parasite is beginning to develop a resistance."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1091000,"text":"The reason I say this"},{"time":1093000,"text":"is because we have to know"},{"time":1095000,"text":"that organized crime"},{"time":1097000,"text":"impacts all sorts of areas of our lives."},{"time":1100000,"text":"You don't have to sleep with prostitutes"},{"time":1103000,"text":"or take drugs"},{"time":1105000,"text":"in order to have a relationship with organized crime."},{"time":1107000,"text":"They affect our bank accounts."},{"time":1109000,"text":"They affect our communications, our pension funds."},{"time":1111000,"text":"They even affect the food that we eat"},{"time":1115000,"text":"and our governments."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1117000,"text":"This is no longer an issue"},{"time":1120000,"text":"of Sicilians from Palermo and New York."},{"time":1123000,"text":"There is no romance involved with gangsters"},{"time":1126000,"text":"in the 21st Century."},{"time":1128000,"text":"This is a mighty industry,"},{"time":1131000,"text":"and it creates instability and violence"},{"time":1134000,"text":"wherever it goes."},{"time":1136000,"text":"It is a major economic force"},{"time":1138000,"text":"and we need to take it very, very seriously."},{"time":1142000,"text":"It's been a privilege talking to you."},{"time":1144000,"text":"Thank you very much."},{"time":1146000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}